data.name: Special Schedule
data.desc: Target 1 Machine monster in your GY with 3000 or more ATK; Special Summon that target in Defense Position. If this Set card is sent from the field to the GY: You can target 1 Level 10 Machine monster in your GY; add that target to your hand. You can only activate 1 "Special Schedule" per turn.
